attributes.review: ok so i got the app thinking it was a great idea.. you know. just got it because of popular recommendations. only to be extremely ✨disappointed✨ with the quality. everything was fine until about two hours after getting the app, Jeffrey epstein shows up in my room telling me that i’m awful and he slaps me in the face. very rude if you ask me🙄. i later start getting coronavirus symptoms and i start seeing sparkles...but not just any sparkles. they were sparkles from above. that’s right...donald’s own mother came to visit me saying that she was very disappointed in her son. saying that he wasn’t a very bright student, and he had always dreamed of becoming a custodian for the nearby public school. then she goes on for at least an hour about his whole life and how he lived in her basement for 4 years in his twenty’s. with this information, i said goodbye to her and went to bed. the next day, i’m yet again faced with an insane situation! a spirit looking donald trump comes into my room saying that i need to be misogynistic, racist, homophobic, etc. or i will die!!! i agree out of fear for my life. he then proceeds to slap me in the face after repeating these things for 20 minutes straight in a very hypnotic tone. after the third traumatic experience i had in the past 24 hours, he flys away, joined by his great buddy jeffery epstein. as they fly away into the sunset, everything became so clear... i ran to my phone and deleted the app, and sat in the corner for two hours listening to sad songs until finally bringing myself to write this review. and that brings me to right now. awful app. highly don’t recommend if you don’t want the experience i had. anyway, back to tiktok where my whole soul is, so don’t delete it or the power of gen z will overrule you for good. thank you so much for your time😊😻✨💅❤️🩱
